data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully remodeled townhome in a prime location. Minutes from downtown Bentonville, head home hit the lake in your kayak or mountain bike trail then sit on your porch and grill dinner. No yard to upkeep, access to pools, golf courses, lakes, gym, parks, playgrounds, rec room tennis & trails. This easy keeper 2 bedroom, 1.5 bath is designed for quiet relaxing comfort in the middle of the action. Newer roof, carpet, water heater, appliances, and newly remodeled bathrooms. If you're looking for a wonderful home with no landscape maintenance for yourself, or as an investment, look no further!
